    "client_msg_id": "91581f57-f85c-48cb-94b7-6bee2052ce40",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I thought you did a very good job at creating a rudimentary 5 pane tiled interface. If you wish i can give you some feedback on the interface, where numerous sub-optimal decisions were made. One of the biggest problems with the project is that in the case of the square being redrawn you picked an application which is too simple to be a good test. I suggest you pick a series of apps, in a progression like clock, wristwatch, snake, tictactoe, minesweeper, chess. You can't tell how good an idea is at the \"hello world\" level, you have to take on a tougher problem to see how it pans out.",
